    "title": "Mkate kutoka Mbinguni",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mkate kutoka mbinguni",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Wakati Waisraeli walipoondoka Misri na kuingia nyikani, Mungu aliwapa mana. Mana ilikuwa ni kitu kama mkate ambacho Mungu aliwapa kula (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:1-Exod16:36\">Kutoka 16</a>). BWANA aliwapa chakula cha kutosha kwa mahitaji yao ya kila siku (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20-Neh9:21\">Nehemia 9:20–21</a>). Huu &quot;mkate kutoka mbinguni&quot; ulionyesha upendo wa Mungu na ulionyesha utunzaji wake maalum kwa Israeli katika nyika (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:16\">16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:24\">Zaburi 78:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:40\">105:40</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:17\">Ufunuo 2:17</a>).</p><p>Manna ilikuwa chakula halisi, lakini vifungu vingine vinautumia kwa njia ya ishara. Inawakilisha uhusiano wa kiroho na Mungu. Ni ishara ya utoaji wa miujiza wa Mungu kwa watu wake (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:3-1Cor10:4\">1 Wakorintho 10:3–4</a>). Wakati huo huo, manna inahusishwa na malalamiko ya Waisraeli dhidi ya Mungu na ukosefu wao wa imani katika utoaji wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1-Num11:15\">Hesabu 11:1–15</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:5\">1 Wakorintho 10:5</a>).</p><p>Yesu aliwalisha kwa muujiza takribani wanaume 5,000 karibu na Bahari ya Galilaya, mbali na wanawake na watoto.. Kisha akafundisha katika sinagogi huko Kapernaumu kuhusu “mkate wa uzima” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:22-John6:59\">Yohana 6:22–59</a>). Alijiita “mkate wa kweli kutoka mbinguni” na “mkate wa uzima” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:32-John6:35\">Yohana 6:32–35</a>). Alionyesha uhusiano kati ya uzima wa milele na hitaji la kula &quot;Mwili Wangu na kunywa Damu Yangu” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:50-John6:58\">Yohana 6:50–58</a>). Mana ilitoa chakula nyikani, lakini Yesu ni mkate wa kweli kutoka kwa Mungu, anayetoa chakula cha kiroho na nguvu. Hitaji la chakula la Waisraeli liliwanyenyekeza nyikani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 8:3</a>). Sasa, wafuasi wa Yesu lazima wajinyenyekeze na kupokea utimilifu wa maisha yake kwa imani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:35-John6:40\">Yohana 6:35–40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:47-John6:51\">47–51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:63-John6:64\">63–64</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:1-Exod16:36\">Kutoka 16:1–36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:1-Num11:15\">Hesabu 11:1–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:16\">16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:10-Josh5:12\">Yoshua 5:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20-Neh9:21\">Nehemia 9:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:24\">Zaburi 78:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:40\">105:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:1-John6:15\">Yohana 6:1–15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:22-John6:64\">22–64</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:3-1Cor10:5\">1 Wakorintho 10:3–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:17\">Ufunuo 2:17</a></p>",
